<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="brave-adj">brave <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /breɪv/    美 /breɪv/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>勇敢的；无畏的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>as brave as a lion
勇猛如狮</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>It was brave of</strong> you <strong>to</strong> speak in front of all those people. 
能在那些人面前讲话，你很勇敢。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>bravely   /'breɪvli/ adv   </p>
<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>It was <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (勇敢的) of Mary to quit her job and start her own business.  （2014 陕西）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. brave  </p></div>